							"extension": [
								{
									"url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/questionnaire-instruction",
									"valueString": "Think about days you were limited in the amount or kind of work you could do, days you accomplished less than you would like, or days you could not do your work as carefully as usual. If hepatitis C affected your work only a little, choose a low number. Choose a high number if hepatitis C affected your work a great deal."
